#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:8
#, no-c-format
msgid "Online Help"
msgstr "Online-hulp"

#. Tag: date
#: index.docbook:11
#, no-c-format
msgid "2018-04-01"
msgstr "2018-04-01"

#. Tag: releaseinfo
#: index.docbook:12
#, no-c-format
msgid "Applications 18.04"
msgstr "Applications 18.04"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:16
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On this page, you can find different ways to find online help and additional "
"information provided by the &kde; community."
msgstr ""
"Op deze pagina vindt u verschillende manieren om online-hulp en extra "
"informatie geleverd door de &kde;-gemeenschap te vinden."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:20
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kde; UserBase"
msgstr "&kde; UserBase"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:21
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<ulink url=\"https://userbase.kde.org/Special:myLanguage/"
"An_introduction_to_KDE\">An Introduction to &kde;</ulink>&nbsp;"
msgstr ""
"<ulink url=\"https://userbase.kde.org/Special:myLanguage/"
"An_introduction_to_KDE\">Een introductie in &kde;</ulink>&nbsp;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:25
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Learn more about the <ulink url=\"https://kde.org/community/whatiskde/\"> "
"&kde; community and its software</ulink> and find information to help you "
"get started. Also, discover what <ulink url=\"https://userbase.kde.org/"
"Special:myLanguage/Welcome_to_KDE_UserBase\"> UserBase</ulink> is and how it "
"can help you."
msgstr ""
"Leer meer over de <ulink url=\"https://kde.org/community/whatiskde/\"> &kde;-"
"gemeenschap en zijn software</ulink> en zoek informatie om u op weg te "
"helpen. Ontdek ook wat <ulink url=\"http://userbase.kde.org/Special:"
"myLanguage/Welcome_to_KDE_UserBase\"> UserBase</ulink> is en hoe het u kan "
"helpen."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:33
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<ulink url=\"https://userbase.kde.org/Special:myLanguage/Getting_Help"
"\">Getting Help</ulink>&nbsp;"
msgstr ""
"<ulink url=\"http://userbase.kde.org/Special:myLanguage/Getting_Help\">Hulp "
"zoeken</ulink>&nbsp;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:36
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Need some help? Here are some suggested places where you can get help with "
"problems, as well some hints on how to improve the quality of answers you "
"receive."
msgstr ""
"Heeft u hulp nodig? Hier worden plekken gesuggereerd waar u hulp kunt "
"krijgen bij problemen, evenals hints over hoe u de kwaliteit van antwoorden "
"die u ontvangt kunt verbeteren."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:42
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<ulink url=\"https://userbase.kde.org/Special:myLanguage/Applications"
"\">Applications</ulink>&nbsp;"
msgstr ""
"<ulink url=\"http://userbase.kde.org/Special:myLanguage/Applications"
"\">Toepassingen</ulink>&nbsp;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:45
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Discover the wide variety of applications from the &kde; Community, and find "
"out what program suits your needs and preferences."
msgstr ""
"Ontdek de brede variëteit van applicaties uit de &kde;-gemeenschap en vindt "
"uit welke programma's overeenkomen met uw behoeften en voorkeuren."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:51
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<ulink url=\"https://userbase.kde.org/Special:myLanguage/Tutorials"
"\">Tutorials</ulink>&nbsp;"
msgstr ""
"<ulink url=\"http://userbase.kde.org/Special:myLanguage/Tutorials"
"\">Handleidingen</ulink>&nbsp;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:54
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"How-To's, Tips &amp; Tricks that can help make your &kde; software "
"experience more enjoyable and productive."
msgstr ""
"Howto's, tips &amp; trucks die u kunnen helpen om uw ervaring met &kde;-"
"software nog leuker en productiever te maken."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:63
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kde; Forum"
msgstr "&kde;-forum"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:64
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<ulink url=\"https://forum.kde.org/\">&kde; Community Forums</ulink>&nbsp;"
msgstr ""
"<ulink url=\"https://forum.kde.org/\">Forums van de &kde;-gemeenschap "
"(Engels)</ulink>&nbsp;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:67
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The &kde; Forums offer users, developers and people interested in &kde; a "
"place to help each other, discuss &kde;-related topics and exchange ideas. "
"You can find <ulink url=\"https://forum.kde.org/viewforum.php?f=14/"
"\">Tutorials &amp; Tips</ulink> in the forum."
msgstr ""
"De &kde;-forums bieden gebruikers, ontwikkelaars en mensen geïnteresseerd in "
"&kde; een plek om elkaar te helpen, te discussiëren over aan &kde; "
"gerelateerde onderwerpen en de uitwisseling van ideeën. U kunt <ulink url="
"\"https://forum.kde.org/viewforum.php?f=14/\">Handleidingen &amp; tips</"
"ulink> vinden in het forum."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:76
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kde; Techbase"
msgstr "&kde; Techbase"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:77
#, no-c-format
msgid "<ulink url=\"https://techbase.kde.org/\">&kde; Techbase</ulink>&nbsp;"
msgstr "<ulink url=\"https://techbase.kde.org/\">&kde; Techbase</ulink>&nbsp;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:80
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Information for developers and help to set up a &kde; development "
"environment."
msgstr ""
"Informatie voor ontwikkelaars en hulp bij het opzetten van een &kde; "
"ontwikkelomgeving."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:86
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kde; Documentation"
msgstr "&kde;-documentatie"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:87
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<ulink url=\"https://docs.kde.org/\">&kde; Documentation site</ulink>&nbsp;"
msgstr ""
"<ulink url=\"https://docs.kde.org/\">&kde; Documentatie-site (Engels)</"
"ulink>&nbsp;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:90
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This page holds the complete &kde; User Documentation in over 25 languages "
"for the released and the development version of &kde-frameworks;, &plasma-"
"workspaces; and &applications;."
msgstr ""
"Deze pagina heeft de complete &kde;-gebruikersdocumentatie in meer dan 25 "
"talen voor de uitgegeven en in ontwikkeling zijnde versies van &kde-"
"frameworks;, &plasma-workspaces; en &applications;."

